Ovadia Yosef, a senior rabbi from Shas, a party within Israel's coalition government, calls for Palestinian President Mahmoud Abbas to "vanish from our world". The United States condemns the remarks as "deeply offensive". (BBC) (Haaretz) (The Times of India)Trade unions in India declare a bandh or general strike to protest a hike in fuel prices. India is crippled. (samaylive), (NDTV)